      <title>汽车制造商赢得了在电动汽车税收抵免中使用中国石墨的延期</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/automakers-win-extension-use-chinese-graphite-ev-tax-credits-2024-05-03/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国财政部周五为汽车制造商提供了对来自中国的一些重要微量矿物（例如石墨）的电动汽车税收抵免的电池矿物要求的额外灵活性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/automakers-win-extension-use-chinese-graphite-ev-tax-credits-2024-05-03/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 14:12:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>激励措施受到抑制后，中国在法国电动汽车市场的份额下滑</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-share-french-ev-market-slumps-after-incentives-curbed-2024-05-03/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[路透社分析的行业数据显示，自从政府规定三种最受欢迎​​的中国制造电动汽车没有资格获得现金购买激励措施以来，它们在法国的销量已经大幅下滑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-share-french-ev-market-slumps-after-incentives-curbed-2024-05-03/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 12:24:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
